## Implementation Notes
- **Seeding Script**: A Node.js seeding script has been created at [/tmp/seed_inventory.js](file:///tmp/seed_inventory.js) to populate the Supabase database with these products.
- **Data Compliance**: Categories have been mapped to `heavy-duty` and `performance` to match the existing SQL schema constraints.
